nodes.text: An unidentified female noble served as the commander of the Hapan starship Daphoros in the Hapan Royal Navy. Sometime in 44 ABY, the Daphoros participated in the evacuation of the New Jedi Order from the Jedi Academy on the planet Ossus, after the academy came under attack by the Lost Tribe of Sith. During the evacuation, it was ordered to lock the Hapan transport Sharmok 718, suspected to have been captured by the Sith, under a tractor beam, then send an assault team under the command of Jedi Master Kam Solusar to retake the vessel.
